@node "Install"
Move everything to DOORS:BelchBLABLA/

------------- cut into BBS.CMD -------------
*chat     XM010doors:belchblabla/belchblabla
-------------------- cut -------------------

*** Note: I removed the OLM routine from BelchBLABLA use the internal Olm
          or the Olm which is included in BelchMANIA

BelchBLABLA creates by itself files called DOORS:BelchBLABLA/LOG and
DOORS:BelchBLABLA/DATA where it stores the Systems top chatter and his top time!

You can start BelchBLABLA with different options after the Command...

CHAT 20   ...start BelchBLABLA and join automatically channel 20
CHAT P    ...start BelchBLABLA and be private
CHAT 20 P ...start BelchBLABLA in channel 20 and be private
@endnode
